headline: How CVS Health’s New Insurer Partnership Impacts Its 72% Rally in 2025
summary: If you have ever wondered whether CVS Health could be a hidden gem or just fairly priced, you are not alone. Let's break down whether the stock deserves a spot on your radar. Over the past year, CVS shares have climbed an impressive 38.9%, with an even more dramatic YTD surge of 72.0%. The last month has seen a pullback of 8.4%. Much of this recent movement came after CVS announced its expanded partnership with a major insurer and a handful of strategic healthcare acquisitions. These moves...
